Collection: ships
Each ship can have its own document, storing general ship information and referencing the system components.

json
Copiar código
{
  "_id": ObjectId("ship_id_1"),
  "name": "Ship A",
  "imo_number": "IMO1234567",
  "built_year": 2010,
  "systems": [
    {
      "system_id": ObjectId("system_id_1"),
      "system_name": "Propulsion System"
    },
    {
      "system_id": ObjectId("system_id_2"),
      "system_name": "Auxiliary Systems"
    }
  ]
}
